function saveEditorAppearance(){const page=$('appearancePage')?.value||getPage(); const a={backgroundImage:$('apBackgroundImage')?.value||'',backgroundPosition:$('apBackgroundPosition')?.value||'center center',backgroundSize:$('apBackgroundSize')?.value||'cover',backgroundRepeat:$('apBackgroundRepeat')?.value||'no-repeat',backgroundAttachment:$('apBackgroundAttachment')?.value||'fixed',backgroundOpacity:Number($('apBackgroundOpacity')?.value??.24),backgroundColor:$('apBackgroundColor')?.value||'#f8fafc',moduleFill:$('apModuleFill')?.value||'#ffffff',moduleBorder:$('apModuleBorder')?.value||'#111827',buttonFill:$('apButtonFill')?.value||'#ffffff',buttonText:$('apButtonText')?.value||'#000000',headingText:$('apHeadingText')?.value||'#000000',bodyText:$('apBodyText')?.value||'#000000',textOutline:$('apTextOutline')?.value||'#ffffff',links:$('apLinks')?.value||'#0645d9',navigation:$('apNavigation')?.value||'#111827',accent:$('apAccent')?.value||'#26d9ff',scrollbars:$('apScrollbars')?.value||'#26d9ff'}; saveAppearance(page,a);}
